Subject: [PATCH] accept4

2008-12-17  Thomas Schwinge  <tschwinge@gnu.org>

	accept4 for GNU Hurd.
	* include/sys/socket.h (__libc_accept4): New prototype.
	* sysdeps/mach/hurd/accept4.c: New file, copy from accept.c.  Evolve it
